{"tid":1029697,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"六千多名非本地畢業生三年內留港就業獲居留權","createTime":"2019-02-20T11:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T13:19:04.000Z","uid":67237,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b225cc00385020e4a8cc25194d260f32f26cfe58","tid":1029697,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T11:59:40.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】保安局文件顯示，過去三年共有六千多人，透過非本地畢業生留港或回港就業安排計劃，取得香港的居留權。<br />\n<br />\n根據現行計劃，非本地學生在香港修讀學士學位或更高資歷課程，畢業後六個月內可以申請留港尋找工作，或者六個月後獲得聘用，申請回港工作。<br />\n<br />\n保安局文件顯示，過去三年因為參與以上計劃獲得香港居留權的人數逐年上升，2016年有1979人、2017年有2172人，增加至去年有2455人，保安局未有提供當中多少是內地人。<br />\n<br />\n而去年有關計劃的申請人數就有10200多宗，當中逾九成八獲批，超過九成是內地人。<br />\n<br />\n另外，過去三年有超過11000名內地學生以留港就學為理由，申請延期逗留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=338238&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338238%26refer%3Dshare&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n822%2BFslq3%2Bj4herl9tsBg9w%3D&h=b43587e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D338238%26refer%3Dshare&h=305723a7\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=338238&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\n梗有一個喺左近<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c20a3a8d68ed350b9482320128928c388fdedf4","tid":1029697,"uid":144774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:01:02.000Z","msg":"全方位入侵溝淡"},{"pid":"43881369c3eae6560097f93dbfd55cc67bd38af1","tid":1029697,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T12:03:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭：佢地係專材，佢地先會貢獻香港"},{"pid":"8b01ec940dcc487123f8ddf1079bcf3c2b735622","tid":1029697,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T13:18:10.000Z","msg":"150之外仲有呢班⋯⋯然後佢地又同大陸人結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />